{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":false,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"height","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/CSS/height","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"介绍","title":"介绍","isH3":false,"content":"<p>指定了一个元素的高度。</p>\n<p>默认情况下，这个属性决定的是内容区（<code>content area</code>）的高度，但是如果将 <code>box-sizing</code> 设置为 <code>border-box</code>, 这个属性决定的将是边框区域（<code>border area</code>）的高度。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">/* &lt;length&gt; */</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 120px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 10em<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* &lt;percentage&gt; */</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 75%<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"取值","title":"取值","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><code>auto</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p>容器的高度将由其内容的总高度决定。</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><code>&lt;length&gt;</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p>将高度定义为一个绝对值。</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><code>&lt;percentage&gt;</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p>将高度定义为相对包含块高度的百分比。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"标准化语法","title":"标准化语法","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token property\">height</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> auto | &lt;length&gt; | &lt;percentage&gt;\n</code></pre></div>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"介绍","id":"介绍"},{"text":"语法","id":"语法"}],"summary":"指定了一个元素的高度。","popularity":0,"modified":null,"other_translations":[{"title":"height","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/css/height","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/css/height/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/commit/null","filename":"index.md"},"short_title":"height","parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/CSS/height","title":"height"}],"pageTitle":"height | MDN","noIndexing":false}}